graph TD
    classDef human fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef primary fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef subagent fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:1px
    classDef auto fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray:5 5
    classDef decision fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825,stroke-width:2px
    classDef terminal fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px

    Start((Start)) --> HasSpecRepo{Has specrepo/?}
    HasSpecRepo -->|No| Bootstrap[Ask @specrepo-bootstrapper]
    HasSpecRepo -->|Yes| RequestPhase

    Bootstrap --> RequestPhase

    subgraph RequestPhase[Request → Proposal → Approval]
        RequestAuthor[Call @request-author]:::primary
        SpecReviewer[→ @spec-reviewer creates proposal]:::subagent
        ArchApprover[→ @architecture-approver reviews]:::subagent
        AutoApproval[Auto-creates approval record]:::auto
        ReviseReject[Returns revise / reject]:::decision

        RequestAuthor -->|[auto]| SpecReviewer
        SpecReviewer -->|[auto]| ArchApprover
        ArchApprover -->|approve| AutoApproval
        ArchApprover -->|revise / reject| ReviseReject
    end

    AutoApproval -->|[human_decision]| HumanReview

    subgraph HumanGate[Human Review]
        HumanReview{Review proposal}:::human
        Satisfied{Satisfied?}:::decision
        NotSatisfied{Not satisfied?}:::decision

        HumanReview --> Satisfied
        HumanReview --> NotSatisfied
    end

    Satisfied -->|Yes - call @spec-coder| ImplPhase
    NotSatisfied -->|No - stop here| StopImpl((Stop)):::terminal

    ReviseReject --> StopRev((Stop)):::terminal

    subgraph ImplPhase[Implementation → Test Review]
        SpecCoder[Call @spec-coder]:::primary
        ImplReview[→ @implementation-reviewer]:::subagent
        ImplGate{Proceed or Stop?}:::decision
        Implement[Implement within scope]:::primary
        UpdateSpecs[Update baseline specs if behavior changed]:::primary
        Verify[Run verification]:::primary
        TestReviewer[→ @test-reviewer]:::subagent
        TestResult{Result}:::decision
        FixTests[Fix and re-run]:::primary
        Autocommit[Autocommit: git commit]:::auto

        SpecCoder -->|[auto]| ImplReview
        ImplReview --> ImplGate
        ImplGate -->|Proceed [auto]| Implement
        ImplGate -->|Stop for revised architecture [human_decision]| StopArch((Stop)):::terminal
        Implement --> UpdateSpecs
        UpdateSpecs --> Verify
        Verify -->|[auto]| TestReviewer
        TestReviewer --> TestResult
        TestResult -->|pass [auto]| Autocommit
        TestResult -->|needs more tests [auto]| FixTests
        FixTests -->|retry| Verify
        TestResult -->|blocked [human_decision]| StopBlock((Stop)):::terminal
    end

    Autocommit --> FinalReview

    NoteAuto["Autocommit runs only after tests pass. It updates git but does no verification itself."]:::auto
    Autocommit -.- NoteAuto

    subgraph MergePhase[Final Review]
        FinalReview[Review diff and summary]:::human
        Merge{Ready to merge?}:::decision
        FinalMerge((Merge)):::terminal

        FinalReview --> Merge
        Merge -->|Yes| FinalMerge
        Merge -->|No| Reject((Don't merge)):::terminal
    end

    StopImpl -.->|retry with refined request| RequestPhase
    StopRev -.->|retry with clearer request| RequestPhase
    StopArch -.->|retry with revised architecture| RequestPhase
